(AP) - Dutch Olympian Steven van de Velde, who was convicted in 2016 of raping a 12-year-old girl in England, advanced to the knockout round of the beach volleyball tournament on Friday, even with a loss in the final match of pool play.\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 3007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2714, \"end\": 2716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999959117123478, \"rank\": 4.088298852396164e-06, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 2772, \"end\": 2774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999959117123478, \"rank\": 4.088298852396164e-06, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 2800, \"end\": 2812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9931631249024072, \"rank\": 0.00688393973380596, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde and Matthew Immers will play in the round of 16 on Sunday or Monday.\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An opponent has not been determined.\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde, 29, served 13 months in prison after his 2016 rape conviction.\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although victims advocates, lawmakers and fans have called for him to be banned from the Olympics, the IOC has said it was powerless to stop the Netherlands from sending an athlete whoqualified in the usual way.\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3309, \"end\": 3312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5066796171793841e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 3351, \"end\": 3362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9754513634195545, \"rank\": 0.025127213812953533, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde again did not walk through the mix zone to address the media on Friday, something typically required of all Olympians.\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Immers said his partner's mood was good.\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are making the best of it, and we are really happy at the end of the match.\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we said to each other, 'OK, did we enjoy this moment?'\\\"\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Immers said.\", \"from\": 3732, \"to\": 3744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We knew before the match we gave everything and we said to each other, 'Yes, we gave everything.'\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's what we want to do every game, give everything and play our game.\\\"\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutch lost in straight sets to Tokyo gold medalists Anders Mol and Christian Sorum on 